<<<<<Small Description>>>>> GPU-Accelerated TensorFlow Environment with RAPIDS and Horovod for Distributed Training <<<<</Small Description>>>>>
========================================================================================
<<<<<Description>>>>> This container provides a full GPU-accelerated TensorFlow environment for training, evaluation, and inference. It ships with Horovod for multi-GPU and multi-node distributed training, the RAPIDS suite for GPU-accelerated data science, and a Jupyter-based development environment. No project code is baked in — mount your own code and data at run time. The container runs on GPU or falls back to CPU-only execution.

Key Features:
- TensorFlow with CUDA support for GPU-accelerated training and inference
- Horovod for single-node multi-GPU and multi-node distributed training
- RAPIDS GPU-accelerated data science stack (cuDF, cuML, cuGraph, Dask-CUDA)
- JAX included for additional accelerated numerical computing
- Essential data science stack (NumPy, Pandas, SciPy, scikit-learn, XGBoost)
- Visualization and experiment tracking (Matplotlib, TensorBoard)
- Development environment (JupyterLab, IPython) with combined Jupyter+TensorBoard mode
- Runs on GPU or CPU, with built-in multi-node Slurm support <<<<</Description>>>>>
