<<<<<System requirements>>>>> Before running this container, ensure your system meets the following requirements.

        Apptainer / Singularity runtime
        Linux x86_64 architecture

        NVIDIA GPU with CUDA support (optional, CPU fallback available)
        AMD GPU with ROCm support also usable via --rocm
        CUDA-compatible GPU driver (if using GPU acceleration)

        Minimum 4GB RAM (8GB+ recommended for deep learning)
        Minimum 10GB free disk space for container and cache

<<<<</System requirements>>>>>
========================================================================================
<<<<<Included Packages>>>>> The container ships with a deep learning and GPU-accelerated data science stack pre-installed, so most workflows work out of the box with no extra setup. This is a representative list of the core packages present across builds of this container family, not the full install — run a shell inside the container and use `pip list` to see everything actually installed in a given build.

        Core Framework
